@*
    Design.cshtml - Design-time preview view for PcApprovalHistory component
    
    Displays a static placeholder representation in the page builder showing 
    the component's purpose (approval history timeline) without live data binding.
    
    Part of the WebVella ERP Approval Plugin (STORY-008)
*@
<div class="p-2">
    <h4><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Approval History</h4>
    <p>Displays a chronological timeline of approval actions (approvals, rejections, delegations, comments) with timestamps and user information.</p>
    <small class="text-muted">Configure the Request ID datasource in the Options panel to display history for a specific approval request.</small>
</div>
